title: Revolution Chili Recipe
description:
Try this recipe for Revolution chili starring Le Creuset's new Revoltuion Bi-Material Tools. 

Designed to improve even the toughest of cooking tasks, the tools' pliable combination of flexible silicone and rigid glass-reinforced nylon allows them to conform to the edges of pots and pans while retaining strength and durability. Patented elliptical handles are thoughtfully crafted for comfort and control.

Get the recipe: http://www.lecreuset.com/revolution-chili
